Paper: hep-th/9205002

Date: 1992-05-01

Title: Fusion Rules for the q-deformed Vertex Operators of U_q(sl(2)^)

Authors: H. Awata and Y. Yamada

Comments: 13 pages

Journal-ref: Mod. Phys. Lett. A7 (1992) 2235-2244

We analyze the properties of the q-vertex operators of U_q(sl(2)^) introducedby Frenkel and Reshetikhin. As the condition for the null vector decoupling, wederive the existence condition of the q-vertex operators ( the fusion rules ).